## Governance Enforcement Summary

| Mechanism | Trigger | Response |
|---|---|---|
| Risk hash fingerprint | Every plan at CONSTRAINT | Logged, stored in registry |
| Recurrence block | `count > 5 AND risk=high` | `CONSTRAINT → FAILED` |
| Token budget | `total_tokens > 50,000` | `REASON → FAILED` |
| Invocation limit | `invocations > 10` | `ACT → FAILED` |
| Explicit block | [blockRisk(hash)](file:///c:/Users/Krishna%20Sharma/OneDrive/Desktop/NexusOPS-agentic-ai/orchestrator/src/services/riskRegistryRepository.ts#63-64) | Immediate block regardless of count |

